{
  "stem": "7358.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And on the other side of the river, even though it was mostly populated by Ukrainians, the were more Polish religious in proportion to the amount of Polish religious on the side that we were in.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And somehow, we felt that they felt, the people, that the other side of the river is safer than being on this side of the river.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And since what had happened just to the group of people across the road, they all decided to abandon-- to go to the other side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They also had heard rumors that on the other side of the river, the Jews are better off, and that some Jews actually walk around with rifles.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And sort of, there was a little better atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they decided to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I wasn't able to walk anymore, so they had to leave me behind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But what they did, this time, they put me into a hut that had fire in it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I believe that-- I believe that they knew that the man that we are talking-- the man that is walking around with the [? sound ?] of the rifle, was my uncle.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But they didn't tell me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So I believed that they were-- perhaps they were afraid they were going to be punished, [SOBBING] so suddenly they started to treat me nice.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So they put me into one of the huts with a fire, and actually left-- they left me some food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they said that as soon as they got over to the other side of the river, they will see what could be done.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Perhaps someone could come and save me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they left me there alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was left all alone in the woods in this hut, like a log cabin.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
